Getting Started

Installation:
Download the project files.
Open the project in your preferred IDE (e.g., IntelliJ IDEA, Eclipse, VS Code).
Ensure you have Java installed (JDK 8 or higher).

Running the Application:
Compile the project.
Run the PayrollApp class to start the application.

User Guide

Login Screen:
Enter your User ID and Password.
Select your User Type (Admin or Employee).
Click "Login" to proceed.

Admin Features:
Employee Management: Add, edit, and delete employee records.
Payroll Management: Calculate payroll and view payroll information.
Generate Reports: Generate various reports for HR and payroll.

Employee Features:
Enter Hours Worked: Log your hours worked.
Enter PTO: Log your personal time off.
Calculate Paycheck: Calculate your paycheck based on logged hours and PTO.

FAQ
What if I forget my password?
Contact your system administrator to reset your password.

How do I add a new employee?
Admin users can add new employees through the Employee Management screen.

How do I calculate payroll?
Admin users can calculate payroll through the Payroll Management screen.
